{"tid":527592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實好易分一個女仔係咪處","createTime":"2018-01-12T22:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T06:19:50.000Z","uid":24615,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65afd37afc7e31d6e17f8dda36b8fecada32e434","tid":527592,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:50:56.000Z","msg":"18 22歲靚女/正常樣（總之唔會識唔到男仔）   <br />\n但好耐唔拍拖/唔介意單身/冇特別想要仔。<br />\n<br />\n9成係處<br />\n<br />\n仲有同tb一齊既 都7成係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因係女仔其實係咸濕過男人，試過第一次之後冇咩可能戒到（就好似戒j咁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而另一方面，搵男朋友中意搵大隻/少肥肥仔既就多唔係處。<br />\n<br />\n原因係處同非處（男女都係）既揀偶條件係完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n所以d大隻仔可以吸引好多公廁，但未必食到真乖乖女<br />\n斯文靚仔就吸引d處，但唔會特別吸引d老江湖"},{"pid":"58b971f7b4993916c7cceea8046c5f4de7f4109f","tid":527592,"uid":72454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"8b5c11e647c15746a47d5d69b838fd528a4749aa","tid":527592,"uid":72454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"ab8a5e7fd08c545a8a0aa432945f8f24383971d8","tid":527592,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:58:24.000Z","msg":"seems legit"},{"pid":"b1403a36b434516ac3c33039b31ffe8314543b55","tid":527592,"uid":5995,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T23:16:03.000Z","msg":"點分男仔係咪處"},{"pid":"00e2ea1a7a1a94179b6acf4a3ca496c2662d8caa","tid":527592,"uid":136150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1403a36b434516ac3c33039b31ffe8314543b55","tid":527592,"uid":5995,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T23:16:03.000Z","msg":"點分男仔係咪處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:26:03.000Z","msg":"想知"},{"pid":"fd315be6e6d57ee1c0f5b8060ae841abf2cd79a1","tid":527592,"uid":2161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:29:05.000Z","msg":"睇女仔揀男友身型就知佢係咪處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces